{"tid":644450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會權力及特權條例 明言 許智峯 可享黑警所有特權","createTime":"2018-04-27T08:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T08:08:52.000Z","uid":54373,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b0ea2d16a159546495bed8d68b12fd7d7a73c2","tid":644450,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:50:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.blis.gov.hk/blis_ind.nsf/CurAllChinDoc/1B981112A011C3C8482581460012AF03?OpenDocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.blis.gov.hk%2Fblis_ind.nsf%2FCurAllChinDoc%2F1B981112A011C3C8482581460012AF03%3FOpenDocument&d=ZYVhrGFvApibtd1c5U7j4W6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=47f5bf58\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.blis.gov.hk/blis_ind.nsf/CurAllChinDoc/1B981112A011C3C8482581460012AF03?OpenDocument</a><br />\n<br />\n為本條例的施行及刑事法律的應用，每名立法會人員在會議廳範圍內，均具有警務人員的所有權力和享有警務人員的所有特權。"},{"pid":"0b0493f6cf138af078acc3b23f8d82e02c4cf627","tid":644450,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:50:57.000Z","msg":"第382章 第24條\t立法會人員具有警務人員的權力"},{"pid":"ff15cc2852364b68bbaf233ded9752d09275887f","tid":644450,"uid":54373,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"當警方有相當理由相信，任何地方經已進行 / 正在進行 / 即將進行非法集會或暴亂，以及有人曾使用 / 可能使用武器，警方可以在鄰近現場的任何公眾地方截停及搜查任何人士，以確定該人是否干犯相關罪行（《公安條例》（第245章）第33(6)條）。<br />\n<br />\n警務人員不可以向異性進行搜身。 如要向一位女性搜身，而當時沒有女警在場，該女子便應被帶到最就近的警署，由女警為她進行搜身。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據《警隊條例》 第50(6)條，警務人員可以向任何被捕人士進行搜查，並撿走任何有調查價值的物品。</span>"},{"pid":"a87b62738e06e39985064d6629cfa047d35943ef","tid":644450,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic2.52pk.com/files/170919/2165322_160338_1_lit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic2.52pk.com%2Ffiles%2F170919%2F2165322_160338_1_lit.jpg&h=a3ea4236&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5191e75c2c53e563d18856909396db9a832a7d99","tid":644450,"uid"